Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.73,0:00:14.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lafilia baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:16.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:20.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tertidur karena tegang sejak tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:25.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf sudah membuatmu cemas, Kak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.78,0:00:29.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak perlu berterima kasih.\NSyukurlah putrimu selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:31.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Lafilia baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.97,0:02:09.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:12.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin beliau merasa lega\Nkarena tak terluka,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:14.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia tertidur pulas sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:18.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:21.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahanda dan Ibunda keren sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:24.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa? Tiba-tiba memuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:26.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kalian seperti itu sejak dulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:29.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti cerita Ayah,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:32.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Rovel dan Baginda Ratu tak tertandingi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:35.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, aku baru dengar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:37.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibunda!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:02:39.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Vint cerita begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.67,0:02:43.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal bisa bilang langsung padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:45.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan Vint pemalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:47.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entahlah, hamba tak yakin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:53.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tetap saja, karena sudah lama,\Naku lupa cara menahan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:57.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh? Kau bisa memanggilku kapan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:02:59.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:03.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada baiknya sesekali\Npakai sihir roh bersama Ori,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:04.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}agar kemampuanku tak tumpul.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:09.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Ayahanda dan Ibunda\Ndulu juga sehebat sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:10.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan hebat lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:14.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dulu, kesatria pernah diminta\Nmenangkap bandit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:19.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bandit itu mau mengacau\Ndengan bantuan serigala peliharaannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:21.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serigala?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:22.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:27.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Rovel yang sadar rencana itu\Nsegera memanggil Nyonya Origin,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan sedetik kemudian...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:30.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedetik kemudian?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:42.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serigala ganas itu duduk manis\Nseperti anak anjing di depan Nyonya Origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:48.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, Tuan Rovel pakai sihir roh tornado
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:53.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk melempar bandit dan serigala ke tanah
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:55.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan melumpuhkan mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasihan serigalanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:04:00.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat itu, kami berhasil\Nmenangkap bandit dengan mudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:03.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Rovel dan Baginda Ratu memang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, sihir tornado?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:07.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:14.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahanda sering pakai sihir es,\Ntapi bisa sihir angin juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:17.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa pakai selama ada Ori.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:21.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya Ori bisa ciptakan seluruh elemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:22.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:28.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, aku baru bisa pakai sihir\Nsetelah kontrak dengan Ori.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:30.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:34.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, Ellen tak boleh sembarangan\Nkontrak dengan orang lain, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:36.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:41.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ellen tak perlu kontrak dengan siapa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:46.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya ampun. Rovel berhati sempit, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:48.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habisnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahanda, aku sesak napas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:52.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:57.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Lafilia sudah sadar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:02.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lafilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:04.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gadielle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah kau selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:10.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari bicarakan detailnya besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:13.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:15.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, aku permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:19.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gadielle, terima kasih sudah cemaskan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:20.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:34.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau yang namanya Ellen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:37.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar. Salam kenal,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Lafilia...\N- Ini salahmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:41.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku diculik gara-gara kau. Kejam sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:43.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lafilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:44.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habisnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:49.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimanapun, kau diincar\Nkarena menyurati Yang Mulia Pangeran.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:51.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ellen tak ada hubungannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:57.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kalian selalu begini?\NEllen ini, Ellen itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:02.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal aku juga putri keluarga Vankrieft!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:06.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata kau merasa begitu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau dendam apa padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:18.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada. Aku hanya bantu\Nkeluarga Vankrieft sebagai putri Ayahanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.43,0:06:19.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:22.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku minta maaf\Nsebesar-besarnya atas kejadian ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:27.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gadielle juga bilang ingin bertemu denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:31.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau benar seumuran denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:31.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:38.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau kecil dari segala sisi, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:42.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Segala sisi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:49.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pu-Punyaku juga pasti akan tumbuh besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:53.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa? Maksudnya dari sekarang?\NKayaknya sudah terlambat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:57.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Punyaku juga pasti tumbuh besar, kok!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:05.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ellen, punya ibumu juga besar sekali.\NTenang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:08.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah, sudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:13.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Tenang saja, semua aman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:22.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beraninya manusia fana menghina Tuan Putri.\NLihat saja nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:34.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ellen, jangan dipikirkan. Istirahatlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:35.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:37.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Putri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:40.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perlu hamba cabik-cabik gadis itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:43.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Van, jangan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:45.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lafilia itu sepupuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:47.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gadis itu sepupu Tuan Putri?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:51.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Makanya jangan marah padanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hamba usahakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:07:56.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:02.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Putri, silakan elus-elus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Van!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:16.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:19.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahanda, mari nikmati kelembutan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:20.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:24.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Elus, elus, elus...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:30.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin cepat dewasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:37.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ellen, kenapa ingin cepat dewasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:45.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Roh pun tak bisa menahan pertumbuhan,\Nmereka pasti tumbuh dewasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:48.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa tak bisa begini saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:51.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah jadi kesepian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.83,0:08:56.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat dewasa nanti,\Nkau akan pergi dari sisiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:57.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hal seperti itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Hal seperti itu...\N- Ayahanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:00.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah tak mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:05.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ellen! Janji, ya? Jangan nikahi orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:13.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sakit. Ellen, sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:16.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahanda kenapa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:20.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah baikan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:23.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, sudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:31.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bahagia terlahir sebagai\Nanak Ayahanda dan Ibunda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:36.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ellen bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:39.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidur karena capek menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:42.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan Lafilia, dia tak sopan pada Ellen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:45.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Santai. Ellen tak ambil hati, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:48.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kecuali soal besar dan kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:52.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daripada itu, aku ingin minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:57.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putrimu terlibat masalah kami\Ndengan keluarga kerajaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:09:59.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bilang begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:02.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa dibilang, aku justru bersyukur.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:05.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin aneh,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:09.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku jadi tahu\Nalasan Lafilia memberontak,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:12.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan perasaannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:16.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, aku yakin itu hanya sebagian kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:18.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi tetap penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:20.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:26.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski begitu, capek juga, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:28.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena sudah lama sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:35.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya juga sebenarnya ingin ikut mengamuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:47.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hamba tak menyangka akan\Nmengawal Tuan Putri bersama bocah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:49.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak puas dengan kehadiranku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:53.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Tak puas?"\NLebih dari sekadar tak puas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:55.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya bocah sepertimu bisa apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:59.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suatu kehormatan bisa\Nbekerja dengan roh agung.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:05.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku tak bisa ke negeri roh,\Nwajar jika kau yang kawal Nona Ellen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:06.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:11.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, perasaanku ingin\Nmelindungi Nona Ellen sama sepertimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:15.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu, mohon kerja samanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:18.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:23.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini salam manusia saat minta kerja sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:26.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa hamba harus ikuti kebiasaan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:29.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama bisa berubah jadi manusia,\Nada baiknya kau ingat kebiasaan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:43.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:47.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, hentikan! Bantalan kaki hamba\Nmilik Tuan Putri seorang!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:50.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, kok. Ini salam ala manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:51.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pembohong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:01.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia Gadielle sudah tiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:08.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekali lagi terima kasih\Natas bantuan kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:12.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat kalian, Lafilia selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:13.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:18.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia,\Nsoal surat yang Lafilia terima...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:21.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana pendapatmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:26.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di surat ini tertulis...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:29.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan ke wilayah Vankrieft\Nuntuk sebuah misi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:32.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau berkenan, apa kita bisa bertemu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:37.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau paham ini dari keluarga kerajaan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:40.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, isi surat ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:45.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tahu pengirimnya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:48.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya Baginda Raja yang bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:52.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku cerita pada Baginda Raja\Nsoal surat-menyurat dengan Lafilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:55.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baginda Raja yang tahu hal itu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:59.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}memberimu misi penyelidikan\Ndi wilayah Vankrieft.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:04.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beliau ingin kau dekati aku dan Ayahanda
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:08.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan manfaatkan Lafilia\Nuntuk tanya soal obat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:09.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:11.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia Gadielle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:14.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini metode biasa Baginda Raviselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:18.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya aku benci pria itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:25.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin saja ini ujian dari Baginda Raja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:29.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lafilia diculik atas perintah Baginda Raja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:32.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitulah pendapat kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:36.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tak benar! Mereka tak ada hubungan\Ndengan keluarga kerajaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:39.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dalam situasi ini,\Nitu kesimpulan paling wajar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:42.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau kalian punya bukti sebaliknya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:43.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, kami...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:47.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ingin bilang,\N"Kami tak tahu apa-apa". Betul?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:51.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidakkah kau merasa ini\Nmasalah kami dan keluarga kerajaan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.75,0:13:55.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ka-Kau... ada benarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:58.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang kau paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:01.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah. Mari geser topik ke perihal obat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:05.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesuai janji, aku akan serahkan obatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:07.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahanda, mohon obatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:16.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terserah kalian ingin teliti\Natau berikan ke pasien.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:20.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa tak bisa beri tahu proses pembuatannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mohon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:22.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:24.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:28.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa beri tahu detail obat ini\Npada keluarga kerajaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:33.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski kuberi tahu detail dan tekniknya,\Nkalian takkan paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:35.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:39.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kalian tak bisa buat obat ini\Ndi dunia manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:41.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa katamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:46.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kalian berasumsi roh\Ndi negeri roh bisa membuatnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:48.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jawabannya tidak bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:51.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, obat macam apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:53.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa beri tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:59.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa coba tanya pada roh milikmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau membawanya ke sini untuk itu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:03.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:11.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asht. Tolong, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:15.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:23.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hu, benda ini tak ada di dunia manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:26.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti, ini obat negeri roh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:30.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Roh tak butuh obat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:34.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, bahannya?\NBahannya dari negeri roh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:36.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya bukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:38.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ash, belum pernah lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:41.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, sebenarnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:44.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian tak bisa buat obat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:49.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, kami akan sediakan obatnya. Itu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:50.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:52.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari lanjutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:56.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Obat yang kuserahkan itu antibiotik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:16:03.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Obat itu membunuh sumber penyakit,\Ntapi juga matikan energi sehat di perut.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:08.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasien harus minum sampai penyakit hilang,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:11.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi gantinya akan diare parah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:14.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hal itu disebut "efek samping".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:17.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Efek... samping?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:19.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sumber penyakit itu macam-macam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:25.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tabib akan berikan obat sesuai gejala.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:31.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harap perhatikan tata cara\Ndan kebersihannya dengan ketat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:36.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika tidak, obat yang kami sediakan\Ntakkan cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:42.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hume.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:44.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Y-Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:49.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanyakan tata cara obat pada tabib di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:54.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika salah dosis, obat ini bisa jadi racun.\NMohon berhati-hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:56.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:16:59.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakek, tolong antar dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:01.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:04.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Hume, lewat sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:05.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:10.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:15.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah janji serahkan obat pertama,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:19.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi selanjutnya,\Nkalian harus bayar sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:20.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:22.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini negosiasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:29.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku harus minta pendapat Baginda Raja.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:30.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:34.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, sampaikan pada Baginda Raja\Nbahwa kami
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:36.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}inginkan tawaran sepadan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:38.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:42.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, kembali ke topik awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:46.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami yang akan urus penculik Lafilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:48.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, kami tak bisa terima!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:53.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kalian bilang mereka\Ntak ada hubungan dengan keluarga kerajaan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:57.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika serahkan pelaku ke Baginda Raja...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:00.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahanda bilang, beliau bisa kumpulkan bukti
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:02.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bahwa beliau tak terlibat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:05.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, bukan masalah, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:07.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:12.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kubilang kalian\Nharus terima akibatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:14.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:16.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong sampaikan pada Baginda Raja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:21.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap kau menyesal sudah\Ncari masalah dengan keluargaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:23.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Percakapan selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:30.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tu-Tunggu sebentar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:32.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:38.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bilang mau bicara denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:46.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika Lafilia selamat,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:49.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku ingin katakan sesuatu padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:51.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah janji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:54.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:56.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika tak bicara sekarang,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:19:00.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}rasanya aku takkan bisa\Nbicara denganmu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:08.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahanda, semuanya, tolong keluar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:11.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ellen, kau ingin bicara empat mata?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.26,0:19:14.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Ayah tak boleh menemani?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:18.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahanda. Tolong, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.73,0:19:23.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:27.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengar, ya. Kutegaskan sekali lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:29.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan dekati Ellen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:31.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:44.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ellen, apa kami,\Nkeluarga kerajaan dan roh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:46.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia, kau anggota keluarga kerajaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:51.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Leluhurmu lakukan hal yang tak pantas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:55.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, kau pasti paham perasaan leluhurmu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:59.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebagai anggota keluarga kerajaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:05.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat itu, keluarga kerajaan ingin pinjam\Nkekuatan roh untuk selamatkan kerajaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:08.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, kami lakukan hal tabu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.84,0:20:14.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika paham, tak sepantasnya kau minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:17.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau bilang begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:21.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena leluhur kalian tak menyesal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa pun metodenya,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:27.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mereka berusaha selamatkan\Npenduduk dari Prahara Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:28.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dua abad lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:32.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah tindakan demi capai tujuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:34.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi itu bukan berarti para roh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:40.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin mereka terdesak\Nhingga tak punya pilihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:46.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita tak bisa hapus\Nkesedihan para roh korban.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:51.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagi kalian, itu masa lalu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:57.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sedangkan bagi roh abadi,\Nitu terasa kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:20:59.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:05.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang Mulia, aku sudah peringatkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:07.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Persiapkan dirimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:09.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:13.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baginda Raja pasti dengar suara kutukan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:17.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, beliau tetap incar keluargaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:21.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wabah ini akan menyebar makin cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.25,0:21:26.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin ibu kota akan terseret kekacauan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.23,0:21:31.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baginda Raviselle meremehkan kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:37.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, jangan harap kami\Nmenolong setelah semua perbuatannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.84,0:21:41.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini peringatan terakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:45.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan pernah berurusan\Ndengan keluarga kami lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:49.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:51.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:21:59.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Percakapan selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.54,0:22:02.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ellen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:10.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.34,0:22:13.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ingin mengobrol denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:16.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku tak diizinkan
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.66,0:22:18.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lakukan hal sesederhana ini?
